<main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <header class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Welcome to <span class="text-sky-600">The English AI Database</span></h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-700">Helping students learn with AI while maintaining academic integrity and strong learning habits.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
        <a href="skills.html" class="inline-block px-5 py-3 bg-sky-600 text-white rounded-lg shadow hover:opacity-95">Explore Skills</a>
        <a href="guidelines.html" class="inline-block px-5 py-3 border border-sky-600 text-sky-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-50">Read Guidelines</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-100 p-6 shadow">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">What is The English AI Database?</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">The English AI Database is a webpage where students can use AI as a supplement to their learning. For each grade level, there are multiple AI's recommended for use as well as the guidelines for proper usage. Teachers will be able to guide students in an educative way on the incorporation of AI into school lives as well as establish an environment consistent with the growing change and cultivation of AI. Students can now access different AI's and explore different parts of their curriculum in which they would need to use that certain AI for, while maintaining academic integrity.</p>
        <hr class="my-4"/>
        <h4 class="font-semibold">How can I use The English AI Database?</h4>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside mt-2 text-slate-700 space-y-1">
          <li>Click on the "Skills" page on the top right corner</li>
          <li>Choose the grade level you are currently in</li>
          <li>If you are looking to write a resume, click on "Resume Writing"</li>
          <li>For each Grade there are multiple sub pages which you can use to guide yourself (Curriculum page, Recommended AI's, Disclaimer, and When Can You Use AI.)</li>
          <li>Refer back to the AI Usage Guidelines page to know in what ways you can use AI to supplement your learning</li>
        </ol>
        <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-sky-50 rounded">
          <h5 class="font-semibold">Purpose Statement</h5>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">The purpose of this database is for students to be able to supplement their learning using AI while maintaining their academic integrity and learning consistently. As AI is incredibly new and popular, learning standards need to accommodate to fit the new change, therefore this database aims to facilitate this transition between traditional learning and new learning.</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-600">This database is to be used by Edison Township School District students at their English teacher's discretion. Any and all misuse is prohibited.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

